channel.description:
[CENTER]Welcome to the SpongeX Advertisement page. SpongeX is a new server, it will blow your mind!
I know what you are thinking, what is different about this server compared to others? Well, here we go!
Unique Home Bandos Armadyl Saradomin Zamorak Nex Custom Titles from killing a certain amount of GodWars Bosses! QBD KBD Nomad Corporeal Beast Perfect Glacors - Weak to fire spells, everything but minions, including the special attack! Custom Blink - Celestial is brilliant! Custom Dungeoneering (Media below) Dagannoth Kings Experimental Weapon - Drops Drygores and the legendary Corrupt spirit shield 90% Sunfreet - Get yourself a korasi or maybe a fighter torso Necrolord - Make some money and some cool Dragonbone Mage gear *Your name* Devourer - Want a Hexhunter bow? Kal'ger the Warmonger - Primal is niiice :D Full Fight Kiln Shortened Fight Caves All skills working! (No lamps!) Clan Wars Custom completionist requirements with checklist!
Well? What are you waiting for?! Home Page: [url=http://spongex.comuv.com/]SpongeX - Home[/url] Webclient; [url=http://spongex.comuv.com/webclient.php]SpongeX - Web Client[/url]
Now, for the media!
